Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.60,0:00:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name's Conan Edogawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.93,0:00:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,High school student Shinichi was forced\Nto take a pill that shrunk him!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.11,0:00:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't matter if I'm small!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.37,0:00:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My mind is that of a\Nformer great detective,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.02,0:00:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and my powers of deduction are flawless
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.55,0:00:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when it comes to cases that\Nseem absolutely unsolvable!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.51,0:00:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Valentine's Day is a case of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.34,0:00:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows, there may be poison\Nin that sweet chocolate!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.74,0:00:21.19,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The first end of the century in 100 years{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.83,0:00:27.41,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When told to cry, I laughed instead{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.03,0:00:39.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The first end of the century\Nin a long, long time{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.18,0:00:45.59,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We're leaping into a wide open world{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.17,0:00:52.18,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The things I tried to\Nunderstand as a child{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.34,0:00:58.61,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}remain a mystery even as an adult{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.89,0:01:04.61,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm neither a hotshot\Nnor especially great{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.89,0:01:11.03,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All I understand is\Nthe pounding of my heart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.19,0:01:16.92,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's neither an answer nor the truth{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.20,0:01:23.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All I have faith in is\Nthe pounding of my heart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.29,0:01:28.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That and nothing else {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.00,0:01:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Valentine Murder Case.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.71,0:01:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what are you going to do, Ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.30,0:01:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.59,0:01:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your chocolate for Valentine's Day!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.26,0:02:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This huge event only comes\Nonce a year, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.97,0:02:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to use chocolate\Nto capture men's hearts!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.23,0:02:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.85,0:02:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're, like, spacing out or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.11,0:02:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.61,0:02:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! What about him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.44,0:02:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's "him"?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.32,0:02:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.32,0:02:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those two guys who tried to pick us up\Nat the coffee shop that one Sunday!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.20,0:02:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.12,0:02:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They said they were both medical\Nstudents at Beika University!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.25,0:02:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially Minagawa-san!\NHe's totally cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.96,0:02:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The other one was\NWakamatsu-san, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.42,0:02:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's perfect for you, Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.67,0:02:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He seemed really interested\Nin you, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.14,0:02:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello there, Ran-san!\NI've been looking for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.19,0:02:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What good timing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.06,0:02:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.65,0:02:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll solve any case at all,\Nno matter how difficult it may be!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.32,0:03:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you have any problems,\Njust leave it to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.57,0:03:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan! Stop loafing around and help!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.16,0:03:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm high school detective Shinichi Kudo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.42,0:03:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not about to play games\Nwith a bunch of pipsqueaks!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.63,0:03:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.67,0:03:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran-san! I'm here today\Nto ask you something important!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.35,0:03:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.14,0:03:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here to ask you on a date!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.31,0:03:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Date?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.81,0:03:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you come with me\Nto tomorrow's Valentine party?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.48,0:03:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Valentine party?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.40,0:03:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Girls are supposed to give\Nchocolate to a boy they like,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.11,0:03:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and if the boy feels\Nthe same way for her,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.99,0:03:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he will eat the chocolate\Nright there on the spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.07,0:03:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, will Minagawa-san be coming too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.74,0:03:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course. The party is taking place\Nat his house, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.16,0:03:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll come! Ran and\NI will both come for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.00,0:03:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.29,0:03:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.88,0:04:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is great! Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.05,0:04:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Valentine party? Gimme a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.43,0:04:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, I will come\Npick you up tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.81,0:04:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.10,0:04:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you say that without asking me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.86,0:04:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I was right after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.57,0:04:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You like Shinichi-kun, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.32,0:04:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're being faithful to him
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.53,0:04:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and giving all other guys\Nthe old "no thank you" routine!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.99,0:04:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid! Who would actually\Nlike that big mystery geek?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.33,0:04:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.50,0:04:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you'll go to\Nthe Valentine party, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.71,0:04:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I'll go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.13,0:04:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! It's decided!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.25,0:04:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just you watch, Katsuhiko Minagawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.42,0:04:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use my chocolate to melt\Neven your bone marrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.30,0:04:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sonoko has a new obsession...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.89,0:04:53.35,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Mori Detective Agency
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.35,0:04:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the great detective Kogoro Mori...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.19,0:05:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.28,0:05:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing much...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.57,0:05:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It smells like chocolate!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.82,0:05:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow's Valentine's Day!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.58,0:05:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have someone to give\Nchocolate to then?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.54,0:05:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.00,0:05:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't be making chocolate by hand\Nif I didn't have someone to give any to!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.25,0:05:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right! Who knows,\NShinichi might just come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.38,0:05:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.88,0:05:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I think about it,\Nthere was a guy by that name...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.60,0:05:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.02,0:05:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.19,0:05:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK. Go and catch a rich man.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.86,0:05:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's weird.\NConan-kun isn't here either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.15,0:05:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran! What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.53,0:05:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're about to leave without you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.95,0:05:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no choice but to find out\Nwhere that chocolate winds up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.25,0:05:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.87,0:05:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And away we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.96,0:06:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.01,0:06:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, let us introduce our\NBeika University tennis club
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.68,0:06:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to our guests, Ran Mori-san\Nand Sonoko Suzuki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.10,0:06:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You go first, Minagawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.15,0:06:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK. I'm Katsuhiko Minagawa,\Nthe captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.73,0:06:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy to meet you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.57,0:06:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.07,0:06:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.99,0:06:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, calm down...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.87,0:06:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Kaori Sekiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.74,0:06:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sonoko-san. You're still young, but you\Nshouldn't go overboard like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.83,0:06:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's envious of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.37,0:06:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's really pretty but obviously\Nreally jealous too...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.05,0:06:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naomichi. You're next.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.26,0:06:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. You really are\Ngloomy, you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.60,0:06:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Yoshimi Watanabe.\NNice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.77,0:06:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then there's me,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.77,0:07:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the strong, yet sensitive,\NToshihide Wakamatsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.24,0:07:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who does Ran think she is?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.28,0:07:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She actually looks\Nlike she's having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.37,0:07:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for the wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.70,0:07:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here is today's main dish!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.91,0:07:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you ever so much, Mrs. Minagawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.17,0:07:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Minagawa-san's mother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.25,0:07:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so young!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.80,0:07:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You certainly know\Nhow to flatter a woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.34,0:07:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, lady! Let's play together!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.60,0:07:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Susumu! Go to your room!\NYou're disruptin' the party!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.68,0:07:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Minagawa-san's younger brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.52,0:07:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.56,0:07:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he doesn't really look\Nlike Minagawa-san, does he?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.94,0:07:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long is that stupid\NRan going to be here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.28,0:07:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so cold and hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.66,0:07:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.66,0:08:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-kun! What are you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.67,0:08:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just going to a friend's\Nhouse but then I got lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.42,0:08:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know that boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.47,0:08:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. He's been staying at my house\Nlately for certain reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.43,0:08:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be cold outside. Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.60,0:08:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.10,0:08:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think someone should perform something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.65,0:08:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naomichi! You do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.69,0:08:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You not hear me or something?!\NGet this party started!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.36,0:08:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not very good at that sort of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.08,0:08:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! You dare defy me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.83,0:08:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just looking at your face makes me sick!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.17,0:08:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think Minagawa-san's\Ngot a bit of an attitude problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.30,0:08:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's good for guys\Nto be a little like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.67,0:08:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, did you bring your chocolate?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.63,0:08:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.01,0:09:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch! Minagawa-san's down for\Nthe count once he eats my chocolate!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.89,0:09:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure you didn't put\Npoison in it then?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.19,0:09:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Sonoko Suzuki, humbly offer--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.07,0:09:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, beautiful girls like you
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.74,0:09:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,must have hobbies like tea ceremony\Nand flower arrangement, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.86,0:09:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Karate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.45,0:09:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could Ran-san do\Nanything so uncivilized?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.58,0:09:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Karate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.78,0:09:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As if such a lovely and charming\Nwoman would ever be into karate!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.54,0:09:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaori.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.71,0:09:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop treating Naomichi like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.05,0:09:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It really pisses me off when you\Nfeel sorrier for him than me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.35,0:09:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean to say you're\Nworse off than him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.31,0:09:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.02,0:09:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.27,0:09:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've become so reckless\Never since then!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.56,0:09:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.77,0:09:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know enough! We grew up\Ntogether, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.32,0:09:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get a hold of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.74,0:09:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you accept this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.20,0:10:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knock it off.\NI only want to be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.91,0:10:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.25,0:10:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you really do\Nlike Yoshimi the best...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.50,0:10:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.22,0:10:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It should be OK, right?\NIt's just her hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.10,0:10:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.18,0:10:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to take the initiative!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.82,0:10:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What lovely hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.78,0:10:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.62,0:10:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Outta the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.54,0:10:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.66,0:10:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Ran-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.21,0:10:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.33,0:10:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.34,0:10:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Freakin' kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.80,0:10:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away from Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.80,0:11:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.22,0:11:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Susumu! How many times\Ndo I have to tell you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.30,0:11:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No sweets! Your cavity\Nstill hasn't healed yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.77,0:11:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Kaori gave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.24,0:11:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaori.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.03,0:11:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was Katsuhiko, wasn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.54,0:11:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he do something bad to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.04,0:11:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.72,0:11:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Katsuhiko's nothing but human scum!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.83,0:11:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no reason for him to hurt\Nyou like that, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.18,0:11:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.00,0:11:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn that Katsuhiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.11,0:11:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go Minagawa-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.43,0:11:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Katsuhiko! It's 10 years too soon\Nfor you to challenge me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.89,0:11:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, everyone has to be good\Nat something, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.65,0:12:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran-san must be sick of being\Nwith a guy with muscle for brains.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.86,0:12:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minagawa! Are you lookin' for a fight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.82,0:12:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just call it like I see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.03,0:12:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.68,0:12:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're always like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.37,0:12:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not think about other\Npeople's feelings for once?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.67,0:12:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean you have feelings too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.69,0:12:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.85,0:12:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, that's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.49,0:12:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about something\Nto work off that alcohol?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.13,0:12:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.88,0:12:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Katsuhiko...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.59,0:12:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! You gonna lecture me too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.43,0:12:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would never.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.73,0:12:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, let's all have dessert!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.98,0:12:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, here it is!\NMrs. Minagawa's home-made cakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.73,0:12:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you like them...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.23,0:12:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I will! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.99,0:12:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, is that cake good?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.79,0:12:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both the cake and the coffee are great!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.55,0:13:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bitter!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.22,0:13:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't drink her coffee!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.68,0:13:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here! Have some cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.18,0:13:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Katsuhiko. Aren't you going\Nto eat your cake?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.06,0:13:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. I hate sweets.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.61,0:13:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think maybe\Nyou're smoking too much?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.65,0:13:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should try to cut back a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.65,0:13:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get off my case and quit annoyin' me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.07,0:13:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like I got a little drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.37,0:13:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think I'll go get some fresh air.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.24,0:13:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.42,0:13:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can have mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.85,0:13:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshimi likes him after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.81,0:13:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does she see in him, I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.19,0:13:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which reminds me, do you have\Nany chocolate for me, Ran-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.94,0:14:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Katsuhiko! He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.45,0:14:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Katsuhiko! Katsuhiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.70,0:14:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Katsuhiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.08,0:14:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Call for the police and an ambulance!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.33,0:14:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.92,0:14:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Katsuhiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.70,0:14:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mrs. Minagawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.85,0:14:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Katsuhiko-san passed away earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.36,0:14:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The cause appears to be agricultural\Nchemicals used as food poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.36,0:14:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshimi Watanabe-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.90,0:14:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He collapsed shortly after eating\Nyour chocolate, did he not?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.41,0:14:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.20,0:14:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It goes without saying that\Nthis case is an easy one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.29,0:15:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.79,0:15:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having received word from my daughter,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.55,0:15:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, the great detective Kogoro Mori,\Nhastened to the scene!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.80,0:15:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.22,0:15:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You poisoned the chocolate\Nin order to kill the victim!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.89,0:15:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Romantic issues were your motive!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.81,0:15:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All we have to do is check the rest\Nof your chocolate to prove it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.48,0:15:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! It wasn't me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.32,0:15:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.19,0:15:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything's too convenient\Nfor it to have been her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.36,0:15:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's eaten the exact\Nsame things as the victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.87,0:15:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if the sushi was poisoned,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.20,0:15:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it would be impossible to tell\Nwhich ones the victim would eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.96,0:15:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone drank coffee that\Ncame from the same pot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.75,0:15:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means it was the cake?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.25,0:15:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, the victim didn't eat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.38,0:15:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. I hate sweets.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.97,0:15:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does it all mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.85,0:15:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was Yoshimi-san the murderer after all?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.90,0:16:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.94,0:16:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.07,0:16:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.23,0:16:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there was a cigarette butt at\Nthe crime scene, wasn't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.07,0:16:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A cigarette?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.28,0:16:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! That's a possibility too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.53,0:16:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the cigarette butt\Ndiscovered at the scene of the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.45,0:16:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, there are ways\Nto poison cigarettes...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.79,0:16:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw it! When Minagawa-san\Nwent outside,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.92,0:16:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naomichi-san gave him his cigarettes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.93,0:16:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Naomichi! How could you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.18,0:16:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.43,0:16:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can always find out if we examine\Nthe cigarette butt, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.64,0:16:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true! I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.19,0:16:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've hated him for a long time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.65,0:16:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That damn Katsuhiko was\Nalways making a fool of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.32,0:16:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He even hurt Kaori!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.45,0:16:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I put poison\Nin the cigarette filter!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.62,0:17:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The filter?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.29,0:17:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! He didn't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.29,0:17:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy! My tooth hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.01,0:17:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's washing the coffee cups.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.97,0:17:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.30,0:17:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it! I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.14,0:17:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.52,0:17:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I call this the Anesthetic Watch Gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.19,0:17:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With it, you can make anyone within\Nclose range go to sleep instantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.16,0:17:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His voice was Number 59,\Nif I remember correctly...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.83,0:17:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One moment, please, Inspector Megure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.67,0:17:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is not the murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.29,0:17:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?\NHe's confessed to it, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.05,0:17:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He did indeed plan to murder\Nthe victim, but he failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.05,0:18:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have a look at the cigarette butt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.01,0:18:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of the victim's other cigarettes\Nin the house were unfiltered.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.23,0:18:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After receiving the\Ncigarettes from Naomichi,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.94,0:18:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the victim removed the filter\Nbefore lighting one up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.07,0:18:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, he didn't smoke\Nthe part that had the poison in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.28,0:18:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then who did it, Dad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.20,0:18:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The real murderer was...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.00,0:18:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you, Katsuhiko-kun's mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.92,0:18:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.42,0:18:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How in the world could I have done it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.76,0:18:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By poisoning the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.63,0:18:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone ate the same food!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.80,0:18:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. But only Katsuhiko-kun died.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.22,0:18:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He died because he didn't eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.23,0:18:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, he didn't eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.52,0:18:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mrs. Minagawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.81,0:18:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear you were nearly red with anger
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.27,0:18:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when Susumu-kun ate some chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.19,0:18:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet you let him have some cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.45,0:19:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.99,0:19:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was because you put\Npoison in the coffee
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.83,0:19:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the antidote in the cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.16,0:19:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing Susumu-kun drink\Nthe poisoned coffee,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.87,0:19:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you rushed to give him some\Nof the cake and the antidote!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.34,0:19:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You knew that Katsuhiko-kun\Nprobably wouldn't eat the cake
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.05,0:19:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,since he hated sweets.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.30,0:19:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, upon devising this plan,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.80,0:19:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you decided to use the fact that\NYoshimi-san loved him to your advantage!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.27,0:19:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You knew without question that\Nhe would eat her chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.27,0:19:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being the very first\Nperson on the scene,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.98,0:19:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you took the chocolate\Nhe partially ate
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.36,0:19:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and replaced it with\Npoisoned chocolate!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.70,0:19:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All while trying to make\NYoshimi-san look guilty, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.45,0:19:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pure fiction! There's no proof!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.58,0:19:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there is. In the coffee cups.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.96,0:19:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before the police came, you washed\Nthe coffee cups as quickly as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.80,0:19:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much you washed them,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.38,0:20:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,detailed examination\Nwill still find the poison!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.51,0:20:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if there isn't\Nany left in the cups,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.47,0:20:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there will still be some\Nin the drain pipes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.76,0:20:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mrs. Minagawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.06,0:20:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It appears it's starting to melt.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.43,0:20:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshimi-san's real chocolate bar,\Nwhich you hid in your kimono, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.07,0:20:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.40,0:20:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How would I know that he would\Neat Yoshimi's chocolate?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.53,0:20:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would I kill my own son?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.57,0:20:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Katsuhiko's real parents\Ndied 7 years ago in an accident!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.04,0:20:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you, his father's sister,\Ntook him in!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.96,0:20:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Katsuhiko liked Yoshimi because\Nshe looked like his real mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.76,0:20:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how you knew for sure\Nthat he would eat her chocolate!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.10,0:20:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry, Yoshimi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.27,0:20:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just happened to see you\Nbuying chocolate one day
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.85,0:20:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then the idea suddenly came to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.44,0:20:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had no other choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.32,0:21:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We desperately needed\NKatsuhiko's inheritance
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.40,0:21:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because my husband's\Nbusiness went under!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.49,0:21:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to protect this house\Nand Susumu's happiness!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.77,0:21:34.18,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just my imagination {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.31,0:21:43.94,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Playing with threads around my finger\Nwhile drinking lukewarm tea{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.65,0:21:53.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's walk lightly\Nto the bossa nova rhythm{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.12,0:21:58.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The puzzle pieces are in my hands{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.21,0:22:04.30,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.42,0:22:14.14,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was in the same place last week\Nbut with different clothes{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.48,0:22:21.57,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Step by step,\Nthere's no reason to be anxious{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.48,0:22:27.99,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Case by case,\NI don't care if you laugh{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.41,0:22:37.75,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Beyond the countless days,\Nshe's waiting for me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.17,0:22:42.29,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I gotta go my own way {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.97,0:22:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A lot sure happened today...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.06,0:22:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do with\Nthis chocolate now?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.69,0:23:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran-san! Here you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.52,0:23:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could give you a ride\Nhome if you want...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.48,0:23:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.48,0:23:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Is that chocolate for me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.57,0:23:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No--
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.61,0:23:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you! I'm utterly delighted!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.07,0:23:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.41,0:23:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.29,0:23:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for bothering you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.13,0:23:27.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,For Shinichi-kun
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.17,0:23:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.05,0:23:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can eat it if you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.93,0:23:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Shinichi wouldn't mind either.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.64,0:23:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You followed me to keep me safe, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.73,0:23:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.03,0:24:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sending 25 million yen along with toys\Nseems too much to be a prank.
